cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is about natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning, which are both covered by the Computer Science sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses neural networks, which falls under the sub-category cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The authors use machine learning techniques to train a model to answer comprehension questions, which is covered by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper involves information retrieval, which is covered by cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
